    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they're prepared, so maybe much more details, I don't know exactly what happened.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I remember that there were staying there on the river already boats, also for the Jews that were-- local Jews that were there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the withdrawing, the velocity of withdrawing of the German army obviously was with this kind of speed that they didn't succeed to realize this transportation.",
